DefaultEvent.Description:
Your helmsman gives you a questioning look. You say nothing; you are unaccustomed to repeating yourself. With a trembling hand, she steers your vessel down. 

You sink into the abyss like a coffin into a grave. Stony walls rise about you. Your vessel's light picks out beds of undulating anemones.
DefaultEvent.Name: Deeper
